# qalpha

qalpha is a quantitative strategy suite built to research, test, and execute market signals with disciplined risk controls.

## What it is

An end-to-end quant workflow: from data ingestion and feature engineering to backtesting, portfolio construction, and live strategy monitoring.

## What it focuses on

- Signal discovery across structured market features
- Robust backtests with realistic assumptions
- Risk-aware allocation and exposure controls
- Continuous performance monitoring and model iteration

## Current performance

The suite is currently delivering approximately **8% monthly outperformance** versus the benchmark being tracked.

## Philosophy

qalpha is built around repeatable process over one-off wins: hypothesis → test → deploy → monitor → refine.
